  <name>SLEEPY UI</name>
  <summary>Solana validator real-time monitoring</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      SLEEPY UI provides real-time monitoring for Solana validators with sub-3-second 
      incident response capabilities. Track validator performance, detect anomalies, 
      and maintain optimal validator health.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Real-time performance metrics visualization</li>
      <li>Credits loss detection with sub-3-second response</li>
      <li>Vote and root distance monitoring</li>
      <li>Fork detection and recovery tracking</li>
      <li>Epoch progress and validator status</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
